PrecisAppointment of DANIEL AUDET, of Montreal, Quebec, selected from a list of nominees submitted by the Province of Quebec, as a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective November 1, 1999.
